"link" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/suc-khoe" target="_self">Sức khỏe</a><div class="children"><a class="child-item" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/dinh-duong" target="_self">Dinh dưỡng</a> <a class="child-item" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/lam-dep" target="_self">Làm đẹp</a> <a class="child-item" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/y-te" target="_self">Y tế</a></div><li id="more-top-menu" class="item more-top-menu"><a href="javascript:">...</a></ul><div id="lst-more-menu" class="lst-more-menu"><div class="menu-content"><a class="btn-close-menu more-top-menu" href="javascript:"> <span class="icon-close">X</span> </a><div class="blk"><a class="child-item" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/xe-360">Xe 360</a><div class="lst-lv1"><a class="child-item-2" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/thi-truong-xe">Thị trường xe</a> <a class="child-item-2" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/cham-soc-bao-duong">Chăm sóc - Bảo dưỡng</a> <a class="child-item-2" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/mua-ban-xe">Mua bán xe</a> <a class="child-item-2" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/tu-van-xe">Tư vấn</a> <a class="child-item-2" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/danh-gia-xe">Đánh giá xe</a></div></div><div class="blk"><a class="child-item" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/ket-noi">Kết nối</a><div class="lst-lv1"><a class="child-item-2" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/tuyen-dung">Tuyển dụng</a> <a class="child-item-2" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/tim-viec">Tìm việc</a> <a class="child-item-2" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/nha-o">Nhà ở</a> <a class="child-item-2" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/mua-ban">Mua bán</a></div></div><div class="blk"><a class="child-item" href="https://laodong.vn/ldt/tu-van-phap-luat">Tư vấn pháp luật</a></div></div></div><script>$(document).ready(function(){var seeMoreMenu=$(".more-top-menu")
